extends layout

block Subject
	title= L('title')

block CSS
	script(src='https://cdn.tailwindcss.com')
	script.
		tailwind.config = {
			theme: {
				extend: {
					colors: {
						tide: '#020617',
						panel: '#081225',
						mist: '#dbeafe',
						cyan: '#67e8f9',
						signal: '#fb923c'
					},
					boxShadow: {
						glow: '0 24px 80px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.16)'
					}
				}
			}
		};
	style.
		body {
			min-width: 640px;
			background:
				radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.17), transparent 30%),
				radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.16), transparent 24%),
				linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #07101f 54%, #0f172a 100%);
			color: #e2e8f0;
			font-family: "Pretendard", "SUIT Variable", "Noto Sans KR", "Malgun Gothic", sans-serif;
		}
		#Background {
			display: none;
		}
		#Top, #Middle, #Bottom {
			position: relative;
			z-index: 1;
		}
		.v2-grid-bg {
			background-image:
				linear-gradient(rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
				linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
			background-size: 36px 36px;
		}
		.v2-glass {
			background: rgba(8, 18, 37, 0.74);
			backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
		}
		.v2-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
			width: 8px;
		}
		.v2-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
			background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
			border-radius: 999px;
		}

block Middle
	div(class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pb-14 pt-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8')
		div(class='relative overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] border border-white/10 shadow-glow')
			div(class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan/20 via-transparent to-signal/10')
			div(class='v2-grid-bg absolute inset-0 opacity-40')
			div(class='relative grid gap-6 px-6 py-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.15fr)_420px] lg:px-10 lg:py-10')
				section(class='flex flex-col justify-between gap-6')
					div(class='space-y-5')
						div(class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-cyan/30 bg-cyan/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan') 현재 이 페이지는 업데이트가 불확실성 합니다. 언제든 이 페이지가 폭파할 수 있습니다.
							span Live Lobby
							span(class='h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-cyan')
							span Tailwind UI v2
						h1(class='max-w-3xl text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl')
							| 글자로 놀자!
							br
							| 끄투 온라인
						p(class='max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300 sm:text-base')
							| 포털 화면을 다시 정리했습니다. 서버 상태를 실시간으로 확인하고, 여유 있는 서버로 바로 입장할 수 있습니다.
						div(class='grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3')
							div(class='v2-glass rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-4')
								p(class='text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400') 전체 접속자
								p#v2-online-count(class='mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-white') --
								p(class='text-sm text-slate-400') 실시간 서버 인원 합계
							div(class='v2-glass rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-4')
								p(class='text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400') 가동 서버
								p#v2-available-count(class='mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-white') --
								p(class='text-sm text-slate-400') 응답 중인 서버 수
							div(class='v2-glass rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-4')
								p(class='text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-400') 서버 정원
								p#v2-capacity-count(class='mt-2 text-3xl font-black text-white') --
								p(class='text-sm text-slate-400') 서버당 최대 인원
					div(class='flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row')
